        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'B')"><span class="opt-l">B</span>but also enter the human food chain through seafood consumption</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'C')"><span class="opt-l">C</span>but also the human food chain is being entered through seafood consumption</div>
        <div class="opt" onclick="pick(1,this,'D')"><span class="opt-l">D</span>but also entering the human food chain through seafood consumption</div>
